    "en": {
      "title": "Parliament continues to be in the grip of Budujana Peramuna - Sumanthran reports",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "In his Twitter message, Sumanthran, Member of Parliament of the Tamil Desiya Federation, said that Parliament should continue to be under the grip of Budujana Peramuna.",
        "Parliament has once again revealed that it is still in the clutches of the public referendum which has lost the mandate of the people.",
        "Sumanthran said that the JVP leader has raised an important question as to what happened to the 113 people who openly expressed their support for Dulles."
      ],
